14:51.960 --> 14:54.960
HE LAUGHS,
APPLAUSE

14:54.960 --> 14:56.960
He's back!
CHEERING

14:56.960 --> 14:57.960
Bloody hell!

14:57.960 --> 14:58.960
We don't see you for ages,

14:58.960 --> 15:00.960
