looking like death's door Elvis!

15:00.960 --> 15:02.960
LAUGHTER

15:02.960 --> 15:05.000
Aw, listen, I'm sorry, everyone.

15:05.000 --> 15:08.480
I'm sorry I haven't been doing
my regular slot for a while.

15:08.480 --> 15:11.480
