with primary progressive MS.

15:15.960 --> 15:16.960
It's all right.

15:16.960 --> 15:18.960
We had a Johnny Cash tribute
in here. Amazing.

15:18.960 --> 15:20.000
It's like being in the room
with him.

15:20.000 --> 15:21.160
LAUGHTER

15:21.160 --> 15:23.960
And your act was getting
quite a bit boring, mate.

15:23.960 --> 15:25.160
Quite a bit boring, Barbara?

15:25.160 --> 15:26.960
Well, no-one forces you
to come, love!

15:26.960 --> 15:28.960
LAUGHTER

15:28.960 --> 15:30.960
Oh, do you know what?

15:30.960 --> 15:32.960
One of you said to me there
in the toilet,

15:32.960 --> 15:34.960
"I thought you were dead, lad."

15:34.960 --> 15:38.960
I'll be honest with you.
Sometimes, it's felt like that.

15:38.960 --> 15:39.960
So sorry, lad.

15:40.960 --> 15:43.960
But see that beauty there?
That's our Aimee.

15:43.960 --> 15:47.960
She's been the strong one
through all this, not me.

15:47.960 --> 15:49.960
She sorted me some weed,

15:49.960 --> 15:51.960
