it's like all this is real.

16:02.800 --> 16:05.960
I wanna be the man of house
and take care of her,

16:05.960 --> 16:09.160
but now I've got these fears
that my body's gonna let me down.

16:12.960 --> 16:14.960
And I don't wanna let you down, love.

16:16.960 --> 16:18.960
HE SOBS
Oh, God, listen to him.

16:18.960 --> 16:20.960
Right. Give me that.

16:20.960 --> 16:22.960
I also got him the weed
to make him sleepy,

16:22.960 --> 16:25.320
because when he's awake,
he does my head in.

16:25.320 --> 16:26.960
LAUGHTER

16:26.960 --> 16:28.960
Is there any need for you?

16:28.960 --> 16:31.960
I've just been pouring
my bloody heart out here! So?

16:31.960 --> 16:33.960
Have you got any idea
what it's like living with you?

16:33.960 --> 16:37.960
Every time I try and help, he moans.
Tell 'em all about that.

16:37.960 --> 16:40.000
That's cos
I don't want your help, love.

16:40.000 --> 16:41.960
And I don't want to be helping you

16:41.960 --> 16:44.960
off the bathroom floor at 4am
cos you fell.

16:44.960 --> 16:46.960
I wanna be helping Mia-Louise
into bed at 4am

16:46.960 --> 16:49.960
cos she's pissed out of her face
after a boss night with me.

16:49.960 --> 16:50.960
Oh!
LAUGHTER

16:50.960 --> 16:53.960
I don't want to be missing school
because I'm walking around shops

16:53.960 --> 16:55.960
looking for fennel seeds
cos you can't shit.

16:55.960 --> 16:57.960
LAUGHTER
All right.

16:57.960 --> 17:00.000
I wanna be in school,
enjoying myself.

17:00.000 --> 17:03.960
But I help you because I love you.

17:03.960 --> 17:05.960
Aw.
And this is our reality now.

17:05.960 --> 17:09.960
So we need to deal with it together,
the best that we can.

17:09.960 --> 17:12.640
I get it, love, I do. I get it.

17:12.640 --> 17:14.960
Look... can I have my hug now?

17:14.960 --> 17:16.960
No.
Oh!

17:16.960 --> 17:19.960
Cos you can start with listening
to me about using this cane.

17:19.960 --> 17:21.960
Cane! Cane! Cane!

17:21.960 --> 17:25.960
Cane! Cane!
Cane! Cane! Cane! Cane!

17:25.960 --> 17:29.160
Cane! Cane! Cane! Cane!
Cane! Cane! Cane! Cane!

17:29.160 --> 17:32.640
All right! All right, OK, OK.
Oh!

17:32.640 --> 17:33.960
I'll give it a go.

17:33.960 --> 17:35.960
CHEERING AND APPLAUSE

17:37.960 --> 17:39.960
Hey, it's not bad, that.

17:39.960 --> 17:41.960
Getting Willy Wonka vibes, though.

17:41.960 --> 17:44.960
Willy Wanker vibes!
LAUGHTER

17:47.960 --> 17:49.960
CHEERING AND APPLAUSE

17:49.960 --> 17:51.960
I love you.

17:58.960 --> 18:02.960
What are youse doing here?
Your dad's got M&S?

18:02.960 --> 18:06.480
MS. M&S is Marks & Spencer.
All right, smart arse.

18:06.480 --> 18:09.000
Oh, I'm sorry to hear about that,
Wayno, love.

18:09.000 --> 18:12.960
Hey, come on. Tell me all about it.
Mine's a vodka and Coke. A double.

18:14.960 --> 18:16.960
You may have ruined your chance
to be Juliet,

18:16.960 --> 18:19.960
but if they're looking to cast
a Scouse Florence Nightingale,

18:19.960 --> 18:20.960
you're their girl.

18:20.960 --> 18:22.640
Who's Florence Nightingale?

18:22.640 --> 18:25.960
She was this nurse who, during...
SHE CHUCKLES

18:25.960 --> 18:29.000
Look, I'm sorry we doubted you
about the TikTok video.

18:29.000 --> 18:31.160
We found out it was Grace
that hacked you.

18:31.160 --> 18:33.160
I suppose it makes sense.

18:33.160 --> 18:34.960
It's just,
you were acting so strange.

18:34.960 --> 18:36.640
Why didn't you say something?

18:36.640 --> 18:38.960
