and our little family.

20:24.000 --> 20:25.960
You're unbelievable.

20:29.960 --> 20:33.960
Nice one.
Proper grateful for that, lad.

20:33.960 --> 20:36.640
I don't know why I do it, you know.
I don't wanna hurt anyone.

20:36.640 --> 20:38.960
I know,
but you need to stop it, lad.

20:38.960 --> 20:40.480
You're right, you know, lad.

20:41.960 --> 20:44.960
Hey, look, as a thanks, let me
get you a Domino's. With what money?

20:44.960 --> 20:47.960
I've got my ma's credit card
saved to my Google account.

20:47.960 --> 20:49.960
Lad, you can't keep...

20:50.960 --> 20:52.960
Just put some Chicken Kickers
on there, lad.

20:52.960 --> 20:54.160
'Oh, for fuck's sake, Mum!'

20:54.160 --> 20:56.960
Yeah, well, good news
travels fast, don't it?

20:56.960 --> 20:58.960
